// Phase 3 \u2014 INSTRUCTOR: classes + assignments + per-student detail.
// All endpoints flag-gated. UI in LegacyRootApp will only call them when
// FEATURE_INSTRUCTOR_ASSIGNMENTS / FEATURE_INSTRUCTOR_ROSTER_UI are on.
